<sup>7,</sup><sup>8,</sup><sup>9</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Finn%20RS"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id8"><span class="name western">Richard S Finn</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id8">
<h3><span class="name western">Richard S Finn</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>10</sup>Department of Medicine, Division of Hematology/Oncology, Geffen School of Medicine at UCLA, Santa Monica, California.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Finn%20RS"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Richard S Finn</span></a>
