</div>
</div>
<sup>11</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="El-Serag%20HB"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id10"><span class="name western">Hashem B El-Serag</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id10">
<h3><span class="name western">Hashem B El-Serag</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>12</sup>Department of Medicine, Section of Gastroenterology and Hepatology, Baylor College of Medicine, Houston, Texas.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="El-Serag%20HB"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Hashem B El-Serag</span></a>
